I've tracked this down. It's due to this check in `dom.js` in `findIcon()`:
```javascript
} else if (iconName && prefix && !config.showMissingIcons) {
```

In your repro, `iconName` is `null`, which makes sense, because you've given it only given class `fas fa-fw`. And `fw` is in our `RESERVED_CLASSES` list, so `isReserved()` returns `true` and thus `getIconName()` returns `null` in the class parser.

